headline: Why F5 (FFIV) Stock Is Trading Lower Today
summary: Shares of application security provider F5 (NASDAQ:FFIV) fell 3.9% in the afternoon session after the company disclosed a major cybersecurity incident involving a sophisticated nation-state actor.
